"grandine e ammaccature anche invisibili a occhio nudo. Ideale per drive-in, "
"concessionari e flotte."
msgstr ""
"Our portable AI scanner detects hail damage and dents with millimetre "
"precision, even those invisible to the naked eye. Ideal for drive-ins, "
"dealerships and fleets."

